Title: Bing Maps TypeScript Declarations
Description: Unofficial TypeScript declarations for the Bing Maps v7 AJAX Control.
HomeWiki:
Bing Maps TypeScript Declarations

Hi everyone, this project has moved to a github repository to allow for quick maintenance and be able to react to changes easier. Please see here for a more up to date version of the declarations: https://github.com/Kyle-Muir/bing-maps-ajax-control-typescript-declaration. We will update the documentation here further down the track.

This project contains unofficial TypeScript declarations for the Bing Maps v7 AJAX Control. It is meant to bridge the gap between the release of TypeScript and the release of the official Bing Maps declaration files.

Installation

You can download the declaration files directly from the downloads page.

A NuGet package is also available in the public NuGet repository.

Install-Package BingMapsTypeScript
